  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/2d2f29b9ea6626c3d60cf743827d8648.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are an elite mercenary, known as Operator8.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A distress call came in to the agency, claiming death and chaos on the moon Triton, a location few have ventured to. The money is good and there are lots of aliens to kill, what's not to like?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unparalleled alien invasion has overwhelmed the Mining Block Facility on the moon Triton, leaving only death and horror in its wake. Because of the harsh winds, unpredictable temperatures and strong elements, a large scale assault is impossible, therefore you alone have been called in to bring a stop to this fierce attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/03a9a25ef2942cd27ecc92e4a0d539a1.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash, shoot, decimate and destroy these alien foes as you rake up the riches with each kill to upgrade your arsenal and operator suit. Use a variety of weapons, special attacks and grenades to ensure that you fight back the alien threat as you make your way through the horror filled station!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/6886c32d1de3e3129d5344a871f8b706.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/6886c32d1de3e3129d5344a871f8b706.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/6886c32d1de3e3129d5344a871f8b706.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/b9db15b936c44da0d964f53cf467ff05.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span>Customize your weapons before you set out and at arsenal stations, to give yourself the best chance of destroying these creatures, in style! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your credits on various upgrades and improvements. You can purchase from the shop for general purchases such as ammunition or vital regeneration or spend your credits at the upgrade station to make yourself the ultimate warrior!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/adf8d4a886f2ebee0ba9569c287ffc2e.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/adf8d4a886f2ebee0ba9569c287ffc2e.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/adf8d4a886f2ebee0ba9569c287ffc2e.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/ef0540b1adb81398b37b24444492234c.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With various unique and powerful weapons waiting to be found, you have the power at your finger tips to push back the invasion and destroy the Telkar threat wave by wave!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find these special weapons, and destroy the Telkar danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/9853810fb81572e8342c29ec9c27e83a.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/9853810fb81572e8342c29ec9c27e83a.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/9853810fb81572e8342c29ec9c27e83a.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/e094adddac0d111cded6a69d5da6c197.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need to find and use every available resource you can to survive! Keep and eye on your vitals and oxygen usage to make sure you survive the mission! Your resources are always being used for you to stay alive, make sure you stay that way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/8fcd95dd240d64da393b8b6939d5b5af.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/8fcd95dd240d64da393b8b6939d5b5af.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/8fcd95dd240d64da393b8b6939d5b5af.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/2be70540f878825588919e2e543bb3f6.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Hivemind lies in wait, brooding and planning for the conflict to save the entire base! Will you be ready to face it? With over 15 unique and powerful enemies available to fight, will you come out victorious? Use weapons, melee attacks and grenades to fight back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/4f43176bbbf18e6bb53bad385f733519.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/4f43176bbbf18e6bb53bad385f733519.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/4f43176bbbf18e6bb53bad385f733519.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/a87a43ede35830f4dce6e49c6356ba96.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro - modern visuals provide a new, fresh look that has horror and atmosphere front and center. High resolution pixilation with mid poly mesh combinations, provides an art style that introduces a new aesthetic not seen in many games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/dcacfb4b0b4b22ef4134003e4a3f6bf4.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/dcacfb4b0b4b22ef4134003e4a3f6bf4.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/dcacfb4b0b4b22ef4134003e4a3f6bf4.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/2d2f29b9ea6626c3d60cf743827d8648.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are an elite mercenary, known as Operator8.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A distress call came in to the agency, claiming death and chaos on the moon Triton, a location few have ventured to. The money is good and there are lots of aliens to kill, what's not to like?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unparalleled alien invasion has overwhelmed the Mining Block Facility on the moon Triton, leaving only death and horror in its wake. Because of the harsh winds, unpredictable temperatures and strong elements, a large scale assault is impossible, therefore you alone have been called in to bring a stop to this fierce attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/03a9a25ef2942cd27ecc92e4a0d539a1.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash, shoot, decimate and destroy these alien foes as you rake up the riches with each kill to upgrade your arsenal and operator suit. Use a variety of weapons, special attacks and grenades to ensure that you fight back the alien threat as you make your way through the horror filled station!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/6886c32d1de3e3129d5344a871f8b706.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/6886c32d1de3e3129d5344a871f8b706.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/6886c32d1de3e3129d5344a871f8b706.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/b9db15b936c44da0d964f53cf467ff05.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span>Customize your weapons before you set out and at arsenal stations, to give yourself the best chance of destroying these creatures, in style! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your credits on various upgrades and improvements. You can purchase from the shop for general purchases such as ammunition or vital regeneration or spend your credits at the upgrade station to make yourself the ultimate warrior!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/adf8d4a886f2ebee0ba9569c287ffc2e.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/adf8d4a886f2ebee0ba9569c287ffc2e.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/adf8d4a886f2ebee0ba9569c287ffc2e.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/ef0540b1adb81398b37b24444492234c.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With various unique and powerful weapons waiting to be found, you have the power at your finger tips to push back the invasion and destroy the Telkar threat wave by wave!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find these special weapons, and destroy the Telkar danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/9853810fb81572e8342c29ec9c27e83a.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/9853810fb81572e8342c29ec9c27e83a.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/9853810fb81572e8342c29ec9c27e83a.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/e094adddac0d111cded6a69d5da6c197.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need to find and use every available resource you can to survive! Keep and eye on your vitals and oxygen usage to make sure you survive the mission! Your resources are always being used for you to stay alive, make sure you stay that way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/8fcd95dd240d64da393b8b6939d5b5af.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/8fcd95dd240d64da393b8b6939d5b5af.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/8fcd95dd240d64da393b8b6939d5b5af.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/2be70540f878825588919e2e543bb3f6.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Hivemind lies in wait, brooding and planning for the conflict to save the entire base! Will you be ready to face it? With over 15 unique and powerful enemies available to fight, will you come out victorious? Use weapons, melee attacks and grenades to fight back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/4f43176bbbf18e6bb53bad385f733519.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/4f43176bbbf18e6bb53bad385f733519.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/4f43176bbbf18e6bb53bad385f733519.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/a87a43ede35830f4dce6e49c6356ba96.webp?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro - modern visuals provide a new, fresh look that has horror and atmosphere front and center. High resolution pixilation with mid poly mesh combinations, provides an art style that introduces a new aesthetic not seen in many games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/dcacfb4b0b4b22ef4134003e4a3f6bf4.poster.avif?t=1733653570\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/dcacfb4b0b4b22ef4134003e4a3f6bf4.webm?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693710/extras/dcacfb4b0b4b22ef4134003e4a3f6bf4.mp4?t=1733653570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
